      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is ready for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character and is looking for a great value! While it has significant wear and tear and will require some mechanical attention and cosmetic TLC to get it back to its best, it remains a functional option for the right buyer. It's an honest car at a price that leaves plenty of room for your own improvements!",
