    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently struggles to start and has a noticeable knock, while the transmission exhibits slipping between gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents on the passenger side. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This would be an ideal project car for a mechanic or a source for parts, as it is not currently in roadworthy condition.",
      "price": 4800.0,
